    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some minor paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and carpet. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s an honest, functional car for someone looking for an affordable option who doesn't mind a few cosmetic and mechanical projects.",
