    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride that's ready for all your adventures? This car has been such a joy to own and is still in really solid shape. It runs smoothly and has been well-loved, so it's totally ready for its next home! I'm sad to see it go, but I'm excited for someone else to get behind the wheel. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and tell you more about it!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized torque delivery across the rev range. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate common fatigue points, and the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with mechanical precision. Performance is anchored by an M-Variable limited-slip differential and a factory-tuned suspension that maintains excellent damping characteristics. Recent service includes a comprehensive rod bearing replacement and cooling system overhaul, ensuring the internal combustion vitals are within spec for high-performance use. The exterior and interior show honest patina, but the powertrain and drivetrain remain tight and responsive.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Clean title. Service records included. Well-maintained engine and transmission. Minimal exterior wear. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances luxury with dependable performance. The exterior features a deep, lustrous finish that has been regularly waxed, showing only minor shelf-wear such as light stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch. Inside, the cabin remains a clean, smoke-free environment; the leather seats are supple with no cracking, though the driver\u2019s side bolster shows slight softening from entry and exit. Every electronic component, from the heated seats to the premium navigation system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is dry and runs quietly, backed by a consistent service history including a recent oil change and a fresh set of brake pads. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring you won't need an immediate trip to the shop. This is a solid, honest car ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive reliability and refined engineering. This vehicle has been maintained to a rigorous standard, ensuring a smooth and responsive driving experience that meets the expectations of a discerning professional. The interior remains in commendable condition, reflecting a history of attentive care, while the mechanical systems have been thoroughly vetted for continued performance. This offering represents an ideal synthesis of sophisticated styling and practical longevity, providing exceptional value for those who prioritize both prestige and dependability.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable daily driver, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and out, and it drives like a dream! I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the basics, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today. Perfect for anyone looking for a dependable ride that still looks sharp. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving power unit delivers linear power delivery up to an 8,400 RPM redline, managed through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. The drivetrain is anchored by a factory M variable differential lock and individual throttle bodies, providing the telepathic throttle response these cars are known for. The chassis integrity is excellent, featuring M-specific suspension geometry and stiffened subframes. Crucially, this example has undergone preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, addressing the primary failure points of the S65 platform. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical vitals and performance envelopes remain sharp and track-ready.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
